title: Ep 1982 - Irrfan Khan appreciates Popatlal
shortDesc: Today’s episode revolves around the amazing Bollywood actor Irrfan Khan congratulating Popatlal for his courageous act. He further says that Popatlal is a hardworking journalist and a true inspiration for others.

title: Ep 1983 - Jethalal in a problematic situation
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Jethalal attempting to take out a steel water mug from his hand. In order to relive Jethalal from the immense pain, Tapu and Champaklal is trying their best to solve an uninvited problem of Jethalal!

title: Ep 1984 - Bhide wants Jethalals signature
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Jethalal struggling to take out his hand from the steel water mug. Daya calls her mother to seek suggestions but instead of helping her she ask both of them to come to Ahmedabad.

title: Ep 1985 - Iyer suggesting a remedy to Jethalal
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Iyer suggesting a remedy to Jethalal for taking out his hand from the steel water mug. At first, Iyer thinks to put a strong acid on the steel mug to corrode its outer layer but Jethalal drops the idea.

title: Ep 1986 - Jethalal losses his Business Contract
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Jethalal visiting Dr. Haathi to take out his hand, which is stuck inside the steel water mug. He is seen persuading Dr. Haathi to help him out of the situation.

title: Ep 1987 - Jethalal is Arrested
shortDesc: The police arrests Jethalal and a few goons under the case of road rage. They take Jethalal to jail to investigate the case. However, they soon find out that Jethalal is innocent and he has helped a woman in times of need.

title: Ep 1988 - Jethalal Ka Parakram
shortDesc: The members of Gokuldham society come to Jethalal's house. They praise Jethalal for saving Natasha from the Bicchu gang. Jethalal tells his father that he failed to get the work order from Yash Oberoi.

title: Ep 1989 - Varun Dhawan in Gokuldham Society
shortDesc: Tapu sena is thrilled to see Varun Dhawan near their housing society. Tapu and his friends meet Varun and take selfies along with the Dishoom actor. Jethalal tells his son that he should have invited Varun to Gokuldham

title: Ep 1990 - Varun Dhawan Enjoys his time in Gokuldham Society
shortDesc: Varun Dhawan enters Gokuldham Society. Daya bhabhi asks Varun to show some dancing skills to all the members of her society. Tapu sena come to Bhide's house.

title: Ep 1991 - Atmaram Ki Nayi Chunauti
shortDesc: Atmaram Bhide has invited his uncle and aunt to his house for lunch. When Atmaram and Madhavi move out of their house, the main door accidently gets locked from inside. Will the Bhide family find a clue to unlock the door?

title: Ep 1992 - Atmaram Bhide ka Bandh Darwaza
shortDesc: The main door of Atmaram Bhide’s house gets accidently locked. Atmaram and Madhavi wish to enter their house but they do not have the key.

title: Ep 1993 - Sodhi breaks Atmarams door
shortDesc: Atmaram Bhide and Madhavi are tensed as the main door of their house is locked from inside and the do not have the key. Atmaram’s uncle and aunt come to Gokuldham society. Atmaram asks Sodhi to break the main door.

title: Ep 1994 - Jethalal ki Bhook
shortDesc: Champaklal Gada advises Jethalal to break the temptation of eating street food. Bagha comes to Jethalal’s house and tells him that he had forgotten to sign on an important cheque.

title: Ep 1995 - Bagha ki Polkhol
shortDesc: Bawari tells Bagha that she wishes to spend the day with him. Jethalal spots Bagha and Bawari in a garden. He learns that Bagha had lied to him about Bawari.

title: Ep 1996 - Bawri is in Trouble
shortDesc: Champaklal Gada comes to Jethalal’s shop. Bagha apologizes to Champaklal for his past mistakes. Bawri enters the shop and tells Bagha that two goons are following her.
